Representation of distribution metadata.
Compared to :class:`RawMetadata`, this class provides objects representing metadata fields instead of only using built-in types. Any invalid metadata will cause :exc:`InvalidMetadata` to be raised (with a :py:attr:`~BaseException.__cause__` attribute as appropriate).
